reviews.review_text: Thanks Much thanks to Scott and Charlie for all your skill and dedication, it is remarkable.I have a embarked on a journey to re-listen to the shows I went to in the late 70s and early 80s, spurred on by passing of our beloved Bill Walton. These 24bit fobs are the best listening experience that I have had with these shows since the shows themselves, amazing fun and memories, thanks .
